com.zwy.kutils.utils.baselog

类 KLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.zwy.kutils.utils.baselog.KLog

  • public final class KLog
extends Object
    This is a Log tool，with this you can the following
    1. use KLog.d(),you could print whether the method execute,and the default tag is current class's name
    2. use KLog.d(msg),you could print log as before,and you could location the method with a click in Android Studio Logcat
    3. use KLog.json(),you could print json string with well format automatic
    作者:
    zhaokaiqiang github https://github.com/ZhaoKaiQiang/KLog 15/11/17 扩展功能，添加对文件的支持 15/11/18 扩展功能，增加对XML的支持，修复BUG 15/12/8 扩展功能，添加对任意参数的支持 15/12/11 扩展功能，增加对无限长字符串支持 16/6/13 扩展功能，添加对自定义全局Tag的支持,修复内部类不能点击跳转的BUG 16/6/15 扩展功能，添加不能关闭的KLog.debug(),用于发布版本的Log打印,优化部分代码 16/6/20 扩展功能，添加堆栈跟踪功能KLog.trace()
